cs.NI, cs.DS, cs.SI, cs.SY, cs.IT 

This paper deals with the problem of minimizing redundant information in information networks, which is a topic that falls under the scope of computer networks (cs.NI). The paper also involves combinatorial optimization (cs.DS) and approximation algorithms (cs.SI), as well as the study of computational complexity (cs.SY) and information theory (cs.IT).
